flowchart LR
  %% get_career_context tool flowchart
  A[Incoming tool call: `get_career_context`\nargs: track, location] --> B{Is `track` provided?}
  B -- No --> C[Return CareerContext: available=False, note='No career track provided']
  B -- Yes --> D{Have Adzuna credentials?}
  D -- No --> E[Return CareerContext: available=False, note='Set ADZUNA_APP_ID/KEY to enable live data']
  D -- Yes --> F[Build Adzuna query URL -> call API]
  F --> G{API request successful?}
  G -- No --> H[Return CareerContext available=False with error note and query_url]
  G -- Yes --> I[Parse payload -> extract job_count, salary_min/max, top_job_titles, top_companies]
  I --> J[Return CareerContext available=True with populated fields and query_url]
  style J fill:#bff,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
  style C fill:#fff3bf,stroke:#f0c36d
  style E fill:#fff3bf,stroke:#f0c36d